		<title>What Are the Practical Use Cases of Web3? Top Web3 Use Cases!</title>
		<link>https://securenest.org/learn/web3-use-cases</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Jordan Adams]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 09 Aug 2023 19:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
